             were indicted for <rs id="t18200918-311-off1785" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18200918-311-off1785" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200918-311-off1785" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18200918-311-cd1786" type="crimeDate">11th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200918-311-off1785 t18200918-311-cd1786"></join>, one gown, value 7 s.; two bed-gowns, value 3 s.; one frock, value 3 s.; four pinafores, value 3 s.; five handkerchiefs, value 2 s., and one pair of stockings, value 1 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18200918-311-victim2831" type="victimName">
                  Gerrard 
                  Rawes
               <interp inst="t18200918-311-victim2831" type="surname" value="Rawes"></interp>
